ing: 1 (29 ounce) can hominy, rinsed and drained
1 (15.25 ounce) can Del MonteÂ® Whole Kernel Corn, drained
1 (14.5 ounce) can Del MonteÂ® Diced Tomatoes, not drained
des: "This hearty Mexican stew is prepared in a slow-cooker.Â Posole's signature ingredient is corn, and this tasty chicken stew features both sweet whole kernel corn and hominy.Â Top with a variety of fresh ingredients for a delicious, authentic meal in a bowl."
ins:
Combine all ingredients except chicken in a 6 or 7-qt. slow cooker. Add chicken and push down to submerge. Cover and cook 8 to 10 hours on LOW or 4 to 5 hours on HIGH.
Remove chicken and shred with forks. Add chicken back to stew.
Serve stew in bowls with toppings, as desired.
